{"tid":830211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[坦克轆豬] 數百老兵聚集北京維權","createTime":"2018-09-21T04:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T06:40:33.000Z","uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"881343d4bc6b78c659691d0d4472171b0fe83153","tid":830211,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"美國之音(VOA)中文網報道，昨日有大批老兵聚集在北京中國退役軍人事務部前，要求政府解決老兵們的待遇問題。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聚集在中國退役軍人事務部前的共軍退伍老兵約有數百人，與現場的大批警察對峙</strong></span>，期間高唱紅歌，曾有便衣人員用擴音器要求老兵們停止唱紅歌。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，退役軍人事務部並沒有派人出面接待上訪老兵，官方只派出一名警官與老兵對話，聲稱支持老兵依法維權，並會保證老兵們的安全。<br />\n<br />\n9月以來，四川、甘肅、雲南、廣東等省份老兵接連前往當地政府集體上訪維權，但卻被圍追堵截，其中有人被禁買車票，防止前往外地串連其他老兵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1950323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1950323&d=FSuEM9jv38mr8qdJ%2BqezmMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=08459e68\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1950323</a>"},{"pid":"fa76a9b277b7fae2aa4ce036422e0c896b475674","tid":830211,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"班老兵成日分批周圍出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739c42f0955ded32013bf21cb5889d31882efaec","tid":830211,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa76a9b277b7fae2aa4ce036422e0c896b475674","tid":830211,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"班老兵成日分批周圍出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"大種乞兒使晒出黎乞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e671548953ec0d06cee20ed558c56373ce1783a1","tid":830211,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa76a9b277b7fae2aa4ce036422e0c896b475674","tid":830211,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislik